high_descs: Go to the TV
Pick up the credit card from the TV rack
Turn around to face right side white sofa
Place the card on the sofa
Move around the sofa to go the table with chairs
Pick up the credit card from the table
Go back to the sofa
Place the card next to the first one
anns.task_desc: Place two credit cards on a sofa

high_descs: Walk over to the table that the television is on.
Pick up the credit card off of the table.
Turn around and walk over to the second chair on your left.
Place the credit card on the front left edge of the seat of the chair.
Turn right and walk forward, then hang a left and walk over to the left side of the large wooden table.
Pick up the credit card off of the large wooden table.
Walk back over to the chair that you put the credit card on.
Put the credit card on the seat of the chair to the right of the card that's already there.
anns.task_desc: Move two credit cards to the seat of a chair.

high_descs: Walk forward to the coffee table then turn right and walk to the tv.
Pick up the credit card that's under the tv.
Turn around and walk to the coffee table then turn left and walk to the chair  that's sitting to the right of another chair.
Put the credit card on the chair's cushion.
Turn right and take two steps then turn left and walk to the table then take a step or two left to move past the table then walk to the second chair and turn right to face the table.
Pick up the credit card that's in front of you.
Walk back to where you put the first credit card.
Put this credit card to the right of the first one you put on the chair.
anns.task_desc: Put two credit cards on the chair.
